    {
      "label": "Further remarks",
      "value": "The beginning of the letter is missing but the end is complete and indicated by a sign of a vertical line with a small circle in the middle.\nThe letters l\u0101m-alif have been connected at the bottom with a loop. The letter s\u012bn has an oblique stroke over it. Final n\u016bn has been elongated Along the papyrus fibresly in line 4. Several unconventional ligatures occur. In line 2 the conjunction wa- (and) is crossed out."
    },
    {
      "label": "Content description",
      "value": "Recto: The sender asks the addressee to send him a letter containing his news etc. (ll. 3-4). Workmen (l. 2) are mentioned."
    },
